The paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model involves the use of attention mechanism in GAN architecture, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of feature map loss, which is related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
